title: FirstDialogue
body:
<<if $visited is false>>
<<set $visited to true>>
Do you love me?

[[Errr... What?|NOOO]]
[[I guess... I dunno|YAAAAAAS]]
<<elseif $love is true>>
Man, you rock!
<<elseif $love is false>>
:C
<<endif>>

title: YAAAAAAS
body:
Yee, I knew it!
<<set $love to true>>
How Much?
[[I dunno... A little|Little]]
[[A LOT! You're my favourite BABY-MAN!|Alot]]

title: Alot
body:
Heeeeeee Haaaaaa
Now give me a little smooch.

title: Little
body:
Well that's unfortunate.
I tought that we're gonna have some sexy time.
Now I rather have some french-fries.
